{"tid":1056418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓選代議員 選票僅一候選人","createTime":"2019-03-11T07:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T23:42:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7d1f7d997c13e2dcf616ed5bcce80122776d1231","tid":1056418,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190311/20630630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F20630630&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FNiuVIf%2Fu6affRELz7PmdGA%3D&h=8f8bd2be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F20630630&h=0b9230f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190311/20630630</a><br />\n<br />\n北韓選代議員 選票僅一候選人<br />\n<br />\n2019-03-11<br />\n國際新聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190311/large/a1703b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190311%2Flarge%2Fa1703b.gif&h=471529b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在「選舉」穩勝的金正恩亦現身投票。路透社<br />\n<br />\n北韓全國選民昨天紛紛步入票站，拿起僅列出一位候選人的選票，投票選出最高人民會議的代議員。這個五年一度的選舉，結果可謂毫無懸念，以上屆選舉為例，其投票率達到99.97%，687席候選人的得票率更達100%。<br />\n<br />\n最高人民會議是憲法規定的最高權力機關，全部席位由直選產生。外界未知有多少名會在今屆選舉誕生，結果通常會在投票日的兩天後公佈。而昨天選舉最知名的候選人莫過於領袖金正恩。他上月底才出席了美朝峯會，就迎來執政後第二次最高人民會議選舉。他應會競逐連任，但平壤無公佈其參選選區。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n投票率逾九成<br />\n<br />\n投票約在早上10時開始；到下午3時，朝中社指，投票率已達92.35%。踏入票站的選民會收到一張選票，上面只印有一位獲平壤認受的候選人名稱，若選民要表達不信任，便要刪去該名字。但平壤一個票站的選舉委員會主席奏奇澈指，「沒有人會投不信任票」，因為選民都熟悉並支持候選人。<br />\n<br />\n北韓官媒《勞動新聞》發表社評指，今次選舉的意義在於彰顯人民「在任何艱難險阻面前都矢志不渝地相信、擁護最高領導人」。韓聯社分析，此反映平壤在美朝𥧌會破局收場，制裁又未見終結時，冀用選舉來團結內部勢力。對平壤來說，選舉用意不在吸納民意，而是在於製造實行民主的假象、監測民眾的忠心度，並獎賞上任的幹部，換走沒有價值的幹部，而上屆選舉的換血率達55%。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"09ff3d4bb84282d950cffd576492ed688f7a3b80","tid":1056418,"uid":233267,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T07:52:24.000Z","msg":"選舉係民主嘅表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3434362eafff9f7a8c8976225d658a7016707a57","tid":1056418,"uid":145230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T16:40:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"002b4d5f0c43afcb45bda9a199e0a44fd020c5fa","tid":1056418,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T16:42:45.000Z","msg":"具有朝鮮特色的社會主義<br />\n果然係朝鮮民主主義人民共和國"},{"pid":"36b4b764a95ac4a329a2702f7e7137cbf8bd21a9","tid":1056418,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"果0.03% 係咪已經被殺?"},{"pid":"a1ef8f9b447ee2424ed6de5ab6118e2174741aa4","tid":1056418,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T16:46:45.000Z","msg":"人大831白皮書，袋住先系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b7899ee8371e4ed6d7ac263f66a0edcb28886b","tid":1056418,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b4b764a95ac4a329a2702f7e7137cbf8bd21a9","tid":1056418,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"果0.03% 係咪已經被殺?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T16:52:13.000Z","msg":"個候選人自己反對自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25beaebc4fa4d2df281f8ca10cdc63304d8f79c0","tid":1056418,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70b7899ee8371e4ed6d7ac263f66a0edcb28886b","tid":1056418,"uid":29514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36b4b764a95ac4a329a2702f7e7137cbf8bd21a9","tid":1056418,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T16:45